[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "（システム）",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "時は少し遡る――",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "これで……うん！　いい感じ！\n最後はよーくかき混ぜて……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00021",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "できた！　クラフト！\nミミちゃん、先輩方、見てくださ――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00022",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "って、いないんだった。\nついいつもの癖で……えへへ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00023",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（年末年始が近づくこの頃。\n　私の通うランターナ学園は冬休みに入りました）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00024",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（ミミちゃんや先輩方を含め、ほとんどの生徒が\n　この長いお休みを利用して帰省しているみたいです）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00025",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（補講もないし、私も帰省して故郷の家族や親友に\n　会いに行こうかなと思ったけれど……）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00026",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "よし、同じ手順でもう１回！\n次はもっと丁寧に、ゆっくり釜をかき混ぜてみよう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00027",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（今はそれ以上に、錬金術の腕を磨きたい！\n　ということで、一人学園に残っているのでした）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00028",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "それにしても……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00029",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "冬休みの間、部室を使って自由に調合していいなんて！\n欣喜雀躍！　この機を逃す手はありません！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00030",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "不肖レスナ、皆さんが戻って来るまで\nこの大切な部室を誠心誠意守ってみせます！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00031",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "きゃあ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00032",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "は、はは、はい！　どちら様でしょうか！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00033",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "あっ！　見つけた！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00034",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "えっ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00035",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "レスナちゃーん！　遊びに来たよー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00036",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "そ、その声は――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00037",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "イザナちゃん！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00038",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "会いたかったよ、レスナちゃん！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00039",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "レスナ・シュテルネンリヒト",
		"romanized_name": "Resna Sternenlicht",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ランターナ学園、錬金術科の１年生。\n錬金術を愛しており、日々研鑽に励んでいる",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]